description: UIUX standards — spacing, hierarchy, typography, colors, motion, layout
globs: src/**/*.tsx

## UIUX Rules
1. Page title: text-2xl font-semibold
2. Section title: text-lg font-semibold
3. Body: text-sm
4. Caption: text-xs text-neutral-500
5. Spacing: Tailwind scale (4 = 16px base)
6. Cards: rounded-xl, border, bg-white
7. Colors: primary = blue, success = green, warning = amber, error = red
8. No emojis — use initial-letter boxes or text badges
9. Animations: Framer Motion, 0.2-0.3s, fade+slide-up pattern
10. Dark mode: always support with dark: prefix
11. Responsive: mobile-first, test at 375/768/1024/1440
